                 Simple Mental Model


| Class                  | Role                        | Similar to           |
| ---------------------- | --------------------------- | -------------------- |
| `SQLDatabase`          | Database connection wrapper | JDBC/DataSource      |
| `ListSQLDatabaseTool`  | Shows tables                | `SHOW TABLES`        |
| `InfoSQLDatabaseTool`  | Shows schema                | `DESCRIBE table`     |
| `QuerySQLCheckerTool`  | SQL reviewer/corrector      | DBA checking query   |
| `QuerySQLDatabaseTool` | Executes SQL                | JDBC executeQuery()  |
| `SQLDatabaseToolkit`   | Collection of all SQL tools | Spring configuration |


These classes are part of langchain_community.utilities.sql_database and langchain_community.agent_toolkits.sql.toolkit.
They are used to build SQL agents that can inspect a database, generate SQL, validate it, and execute it.

